title: GP.vs.SuperBike-TiNYiSO
description:
Release Information:

   Two Wheels Good - Four Wheels Better?

   There is only one way to find out!

   Which is better, the fastest racing car or the fastest racing bike? Which
   would be quickest round a motor racing track? Well now you can find out in
   this highly detailed simulation featuring nine international circuits.

   Go head-to-head with another bike or car, or dual, two wheels against four
   in full GP vs Superbike mode.

   A split screen mode allows you to compete against another human player on
   the same machine and the workshop gives you complete control of the setup
   of your vehicle for maximum realism.

   Which one will cross the line first?
